    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or process of coating a surface such as a wall with whitewash: a powdered mineral substance such as calcium hydroxide or chalk suspended in water, often with size or other ingredients.</Note_Text>
